            article:'<article id="post-77596" class="lg-mr4 lg-p1 post-77596 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-fashion tag-bag tag-clutch tag-fashion tag-purse tag-roundup tag-shopping tag-summer"><div class="post-content"><div class="ig_inline_container ig_the_content ig_before"></div><input class="jpibfi" type="hidden"><p><a href="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/?attachment_id=77612" rel="attachment wp-att-77612"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-77612 size-full" src="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/summer-bag-roundup-paper-and-stitch-picks.jpg" alt="11 Must-Have Bags for Summer" width="600" height="2031" srcset="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/summer-bag-roundup-paper-and-stitch-picks.jpg 600w, https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/summer-bag-roundup-paper-and-stitch-picks-148x500.jpg 148w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/2016/07/06/11-must-have-bags-for-summer/" data-jpibfi-post-title="It’s in The Bag: 11 Must-Have Bags for Summer" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/summer-bag-roundup-paper-and-stitch-picks.jpg"></a></p><p>If there is one item that I am always, ALWAYS on the look out for when I’m shopping, it’s a new<a href="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/?s=bags" target="_blank">bag</a>! Sure this (slight) obsession causes me to literally stumble through my closet sifting through clutches, backpacks, etc to&nbsp;find&nbsp;my favorite pair of<a href="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/2016/06/22/11-awesome-summer-sandals/" target="_blank">sandals</a> (my closet is kind of a mess), but I don’t really care. Because much like a good bag can complete an outfit,&nbsp;my bag collection completes me. KIDDING. Totally kidding!</p><p>But I do really, really like bags…handbags, shoulder bags, clutches, tote, backpacks, etc, etc. So, today I’m rounding up 11 of my&nbsp;favorite&nbsp;bags for summer.</p><p><span id="more-77596"></span></p><p><a href="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/?attachment_id=77615" rel="attachment wp-att-77615"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-77615" src="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/rachel-comey-aleso-bag-zappos-550.jpg" alt="Rachel Comey summer bag" width="550" height="825" srcset="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/rachel-comey-aleso-bag-zappos-550.jpg 550w, https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/rachel-comey-aleso-bag-zappos-550-333x500.jpg 333w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/2016/07/06/11-must-have-bags-for-summer/" data-jpibfi-post-title="It’s in The Bag: 11 Must-Have Bags for Summer" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/rachel-comey-aleso-bag-zappos-550.jpg"></a></p><p>1. Rachel Comey Aleso bag (on sale on<a href="http://rstyle.me/n/bt6cw9mvmw" target="_blank" class="external" rel="nofollow">Zappos</a> right now!) // I feel like I really NEED this one. It’s the round shape that gets me.</p><p><a href="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/?attachment_id=77609" rel="attachment wp-att-77609"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-77609 size-large" src="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/clare-v-patchwork-clutch-600x770.jpg" alt="Clare V patchwork clutch" width="600" height="770" srcset="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/clare-v-patchwork-clutch-600x770.jpg 600w, https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/clare-v-patchwork-clutch-350x449.jpg 350w, https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/clare-v-patchwork-clutch.jpg 610w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/2016/07/06/11-must-have-bags-for-summer/" data-jpibfi-post-title="It’s in The Bag: 11 Must-Have Bags for Summer" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/clare-v-patchwork-clutch-600x770.jpg"></a></p><p>2. Clare V. patchwork clutch from&nbsp;<a href="http://rstyle.me/n/bt6s2rmvmw" target="_blank" class="external" rel="nofollow">Need Supply</a>&nbsp;// This color combo is perfect!</p><p><a href="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/?attachment_id=77608" rel="attachment wp-att-77608"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-77608 size-large" src="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/mesh-leather-backpack-lr-600x770.jpg" alt="Loeffler Randall drawstring backpack" width="600" height="770" srcset="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/mesh-leather-backpack-lr-600x770.jpg 600w, https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/mesh-leather-backpack-lr-350x449.jpg 350w, https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/mesh-leather-backpack-lr.jpg 880w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/2016/07/06/11-must-have-bags-for-summer/" data-jpibfi-post-title="It’s in The Bag: 11 Must-Have Bags for Summer" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/mesh-leather-backpack-lr-600x770.jpg"></a></p><p>3. Loeffler Randall drawstring backpack from&nbsp;<a href="http://rstyle.me/n/bt6zxemvmw" target="_blank" class="external" rel="nofollow">Need Supply</a>&nbsp;(on sale right now)</p><p><a href="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/?attachment_id=77602" rel="attachment wp-att-77602"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-77602 size-large" src="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/lizziefortunado-pickupstickspouch-1-600x900.jpg" alt="Lizzie Fortunato pick up sticks clutch" width="600" height="900" srcset="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/lizziefortunado-pickupstickspouch-1-600x900.jpg 600w, https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/lizziefortunado-pickupstickspouch-1-333x500.jpg 333w, https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/lizziefortunado-pickupstickspouch-1.jpg 1140w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/2016/07/06/11-must-have-bags-for-summer/" data-jpibfi-post-title="It’s in The Bag: 11 Must-Have Bags for Summer" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/lizziefortunado-pickupstickspouch-1-600x900.jpg"></a></p><p>4. Lizzie Fortunato pick up sticks clutch from<a href="http://bonadrag.com/women/accessories/pick-up-sticks-pouch?___SID=U" target="_blank" class="external" rel="nofollow">Bona Drag</a> (on sale!)</p><p><a href="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/?attachment_id=77600" rel="attachment wp-att-77600"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-77600" src="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/lotfi-serus-bag-summer-roundup-600x900.jpg" alt="lotfi-serus-bag-summer-roundup" width="600" height="900" srcset="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/lotfi-serus-bag-summer-roundup-600x900.jpg 600w, https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/lotfi-serus-bag-summer-roundup-333x500.jpg 333w, https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/lotfi-serus-bag-summer-roundup.jpg 683w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/2016/07/06/11-must-have-bags-for-summer/" data-jpibfi-post-title="It’s in The Bag: 11 Must-Have Bags for Summer" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/lotfi-serus-bag-summer-roundup-600x900.jpg"></a></p><p>5. Lotfi Serous bag from<a href="https://www.beklina.com/collections/accessories/products/lotfi-serus-bag" target="_blank" class="external" rel="nofollow">Beklina</a>&nbsp;// More circle goodness happening here.</p><p><a href="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/?attachment_id=77610" rel="attachment wp-att-77610"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-77610 size-large" src="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/asos-pom-pom-tote-summer-600x766.jpg" alt="Pom pom straw beach bag" width="600" height="766" srcset="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/asos-pom-pom-tote-summer-600x766.jpg 600w, https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/asos-pom-pom-tote-summer-350x447.jpg 350w, https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/asos-pom-pom-tote-summer.jpg 870w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/2016/07/06/11-must-have-bags-for-summer/" data-jpibfi-post-title="It’s in The Bag: 11 Must-Have Bags for Summer" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/asos-pom-pom-tote-summer-600x766.jpg"></a></p><p>6. Pom pom straw beach bag from<a href="http://rstyle.me/n/bt6s9imvmw" target="_blank" class="external" rel="nofollow">ASOS</a> (only $33)</p><p><a href="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/?attachment_id=77603" rel="attachment wp-att-77603"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-77603 size-large" src="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/bando-holographic-circle-bag-600x600.jpg" alt="Holographic circle bag from Bando" width="600" height="600" srcset="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/bando-holographic-circle-bag-600x600.jpg 600w, https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/bando-holographic-circle-bag-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/bando-holographic-circle-bag-350x350.jpg 350w, https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/bando-holographic-circle-bag-460x460.jpg 460w, https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/bando-holographic-circle-bag-230x230.jpg 230w, https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/bando-holographic-circle-bag.jpg 640w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/2016/07/06/11-must-have-bags-for-summer/" data-jpibfi-post-title="It’s in The Bag: 11 Must-Have Bags for Summer" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/bando-holographic-circle-bag-600x600.jpg"></a></p><p>7. Holographic circle bag from<a href="http://www.bando.com/collections/bags/products/girls-gotta-eat-lunch-bag-holographic" target="_blank" class="external" rel="nofollow">Bando</a>&nbsp;(only $24!)</p><p><a href="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/?attachment_id=77613" rel="attachment wp-att-77613"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-77613 size-large" src="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/lizziefortunato-poolgirlsafariclutch-zzz-600x900.jpg" alt="Lizzie Fortunato pool girls clutch" width="600" height="900" srcset="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/lizziefortunato-poolgirlsafariclutch-zzz-600x900.jpg 600w, https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/lizziefortunato-poolgirlsafariclutch-zzz-333x500.jpg 333w, https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/lizziefortunato-poolgirlsafariclutch-zzz.jpg 1140w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/2016/07/06/11-must-have-bags-for-summer/" data-jpibfi-post-title="It’s in The Bag: 11 Must-Have Bags for Summer" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.papernstitchblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/lizziefortunato-poolgirlsafariclutch-zzz-600x900.jpg"></a></p><p>8. Lizzie Fortunato pool girls clutch from<a href="http://bonadrag.com/women/accessories/lizziefortunato-pool-girls-safari-clutch" target="_blank" class="external" rel="nofollow">Bona Drag</a> // Okay, this one is a little out there